%% Diagram: Recovery Sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Eng as On-call engineer
    participant DC as Data center +\nphysical security
    participant Console as Backbone router\nconsole
    participant BGP as Edge BGP /\nupstream peers
    participant Res as Recursive\nresolvers
    participant App as Meta service\nfleet

    Note over Eng: Workplace and wikis down.\nCoordinate via cell + non-FB chat.
    Eng->>DC: Travel on-site,\nactivate manual access protocol
    DC-->>Eng: Override badge reader,\nescort in
    Eng->>Console: Connect via serial / OOB cart
    Console-->>Eng: Identify and revert\nmaintenance change
    Console->>BGP: Backbone restored,\nedge probes pass
    BGP-->>BGP: Re-announce withdrawn prefixes\n(peak ~21:17 UTC)
    BGP-->>Res: Routes re-appear globally
    Res-->>App: SERVFAIL stops, clients reconnect
    Note over App: Staged ramp using prior\n'storm' drill playbook to avoid\na thundering herd
